{
  "stem": "1929.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I would be able to stay with them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember one day this German-- some police, German police, which they had these metal breasts around their chests-- some kind of-- there are so many different branches of them.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They came in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We thought it would be-- the numbers would be up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they-- they were looking for a shoemaker.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They-- they knew-- he found one pair of boots, these long boots.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he wanted to know what the other one was, or where the guy who could make him another pair.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we go-- were really relieved with that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, they just loved the quality of the shoes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now during-- also during that time, my brother tells the story that his-- some of his Polish friends that he used to pal around with, and drink, and play cards with-- they came into the place.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were working off of the Polish police.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they told him to hand over any valuables that he has.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they robbed him of anything that we had left they took.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he turned to them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He says, I thought you were my friends.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they said, be glad that's all we're doing is just taking your possessions.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because we could-- we could take you with us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So that was a big disillusionment there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, he thought they were his friends.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Before the war, they were.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we were stayed there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We stayed there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were all back in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And while we were-- while we were in this factory, this deportation was taking place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They only had one train each day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was like, 5,000, 6,000 people packed on one train.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you're talking about probably 20,000 people, something like that, having to be deported.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
